WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 17]

01:15.640 --> 01:16.940
Guard yourselves well

01:16.960 --> 01:18.420
once you go inside.

01:18.670 --> 01:20.450
Do not let the demonic energy

01:20.830 --> 01:21.700
corrupt your minds.

01:37.670 --> 01:38.890
This is a Linglong Talisman.

01:39.160 --> 01:39.890
In times of danger,

01:39.910 --> 01:41.980
you can use it to call nearby fellow disciples.

01:42.750 --> 01:43.340
Remember,

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
never go off alone.

02:18.200 --> 02:18.900
Set out now.

02:19.670 --> 02:20.620
- Yes. - Yes.

02:33.390 --> 02:34.690
Lifei, join my team.

02:37.080 --> 02:38.130
I'll go with Zhaomin.

02:38.760 --> 02:39.300
Let's go.

02:42.150 --> 02:42.900
Zhaomin.

02:43.480 --> 02:45.300
Alright. This mission is urgent.

02:45.760 --> 02:46.500
Let's head in...

02:52.590 --> 02:54.090
Looks like it's just the three of us

02:54.710 --> 02:55.940
on this team.

03:01.830 --> 03:02.530
Lei?

03:04.040 --> 03:04.530
Fine.

03:04.870 --> 03:06.900
Now we have four.

03:11.360 --> 03:11.850
Let's go.

03:23.710 --> 03:24.780
Everyone, don't be afraid.

03:25.110 --> 03:25.900
I'm here.

03:26.800 --> 03:28.410
Before I came, I performed a divination.

03:28.760 --> 03:30.620
It said we'd turn danger into safety.

03:43.480 --> 03:44.460
What's this?

03:45.800 --> 03:46.570
Scratches.

03:47.320 --> 03:48.620
It was bound by spirit-locking ropes.

03:48.800 --> 03:50.650
It must have struggled desperately before death,

03:51.360 --> 03:52.530
leaving marks that won't fade

03:52.830 --> 03:53.620
for centuries.

03:56.800 --> 03:59.060
It seems to be the Altar of Martyrs of Xingzheng Hall.

03:59.480 --> 04:00.940
Even if they were demon scum,

04:01.480 --> 04:03.620
this is a cruel death.

04:10.270 --> 04:11.220
Why keep them

04:12.110 --> 04:13.780
locked up here even after death,

04:13.990 --> 04:14.810
humiliating them like this?

04:17.520 --> 04:18.810
For centuries,

04:18.830 --> 04:20.620
the immortal sects have known little about demons.

04:21.230 --> 04:22.770
So the elders from the previous generation

04:22.830 --> 04:24.980
captured many demons during the war

04:25.390 --> 04:27.500
and imprisoned them here for interrogation,

04:28.200 --> 04:29.500
hoping to find their weaknesses.

04:30.120 --> 04:31.210
Did they find out anything?

04:32.080 --> 04:34.370
They say demons fear not even death.

04:34.790 --> 04:36.330
The elders got nothing.

04:52.790 --> 04:53.620
Zhaomin, watch out!

05:03.000 --> 05:03.740
Get down.

05:14.760 --> 05:17.690
See? Danger turned to safety.

05:21.390 --> 05:21.890
By the way,

05:22.150 --> 05:23.770
have you heard about the Sea Calamity war

05:23.880 --> 05:24.890
five hundred years ago?

05:25.640 --> 05:27.180
I often hear the elders talk about it.

05:27.590 --> 05:29.130
I've also read some books about it.

05:29.440 --> 05:31.980
They all say our sects suffered heavy losses.

05:32.200 --> 05:34.100
Didn't expect the demons to suffer just as badly.

05:34.910 --> 05:36.300
Heaven and earth are indifferent,

05:36.760 --> 05:37.890
treating all things like straw dogs.

05:38.830 --> 05:39.980
The next Sea Calamity

05:40.270 --> 05:41.810
is less than two years away.

05:48.590 --> 05:49.370
It's a Linglong Talisman.

05:49.440 --> 05:50.330
A fellow disciple is in danger!

06:01.120 --> 06:02.060
Where are you guys?

06:37.520 --> 06:38.250
Get away!

06:53.830 --> 06:54.420
Lifei.

06:56.350 --> 06:56.860
Lifei!

07:02.150 --> 07:02.890
Help!

07:07.120 --> 07:07.860
Yue?

07:26.120 --> 07:26.690
Zhuyan?

08:23.440 --> 08:24.210
How did this happen?

08:25.150 --> 08:25.770
Oh no.

08:26.030 --> 08:27.100
The disciples are still inside!

08:27.390 --> 08:28.180
Guangwei!

08:28.910 --> 08:29.450
Let's go.

08:52.040 --> 08:52.690
You're awake.

08:56.470 --> 08:57.260
Qin?

08:58.960 --> 08:59.610
Lifei,

08:59.960 --> 09:01.020
you were corrupted by demonic energy.

09:01.350 --> 09:02.610
I'm healing you.

09:18.110 --> 09:18.730
No.

09:27.350 --> 09:28.380
No, thanks.

09:29.280 --> 09:30.260
I have a Linglong Talisman.

09:39.920 --> 09:41.420
A distant call won't help as fast as I can.

09:42.280 --> 09:43.730
Let me help you.

09:44.080 --> 09:45.090
Lifei, don't be afraid.

09:45.750 --> 09:47.610
I really mean well for you.

09:48.660 --> 09:49.210
You...

09:58.630 --> 10:00.060
If you agree to be with me,

10:01.230 --> 10:03.180
I'll treat you well.

10:04.280 --> 10:06.970
When I become the head of Wuyue Court someday,

10:08.160 --> 10:10.210
you'll stand above all others.

10:17.160 --> 10:17.900
Get away!

10:28.110 --> 10:28.660
Let go!

10:29.510 --> 10:29.970
Let go!

10:30.320 --> 10:30.780
Me?

10:31.630 --> 10:32.570
Let go now!

10:33.200 --> 10:33.690
I...

10:34.540 --> 10:35.450
I want to...

10:36.400 --> 10:37.260
Let go!

10:38.080 --> 10:38.970
- I... - Let go!

10:39.350 --> 10:40.450
I want to, but...

10:54.040 --> 10:55.090
The Achillea Bead?

10:57.080 --> 10:58.210
That's incredible.

11:26.320 --> 11:26.810
Go!

11:32.510 --> 11:33.140
Go now.

11:43.870 --> 11:44.970
You were corrupted by demonic energy?

11:45.590 --> 11:46.090
Wake up.

11:46.800 --> 11:47.420
Wake up!

12:01.960 --> 12:02.660
Xiuyuan.

12:08.830 --> 12:09.970
Have you really fallen into demonhood?

12:41.750 --> 12:42.260
Lifei.

12:43.750 --> 12:44.300
Let's go.

12:59.400 --> 13:01.210
It's Zhuyan! Found the source of demonic energy!

13:12.160 --> 13:12.780
Lei!

13:15.350 --> 13:15.810
Cailing.

13:19.080 --> 13:19.610
Yue.

13:36.560 --> 13:38.090
Too bad Zhuyan got away in the end.

13:38.870 --> 13:39.380
It's okay.

13:39.560 --> 13:39.970
Careful.

13:40.440 --> 13:41.540
- Careful. - Go sit down.

13:46.080 --> 13:46.540
Easy.

13:48.510 --> 13:49.060
Are you okay?

13:49.510 --> 13:49.940
I'm fine.

13:50.470 --> 13:51.210
Everyone, move!

13:51.510 --> 13:52.090
Get out of the way!

13:53.160 --> 13:53.780
Jiang Lifei

13:54.080 --> 13:55.180
is a demon spy!

13:56.400 --> 13:58.420
Demon spy?

13:58.510 --> 13:59.540
A spy?

13:59.540 --> 14:00.180
She's a demon spy?

14:00.200 --> 14:00.810
I knew it.

14:02.350 --> 14:02.850
No wonder...

14:02.870 --> 14:03.810
I could tell something was off about her.

14:03.830 --> 14:04.260
Right!

14:05.920 --> 14:06.420
Master,

14:07.160 --> 14:08.090
I saw

14:08.110 --> 14:10.140
Jiang Lifei resonate with the skeleton of that Lion-Eagle.

14:10.590 --> 14:12.330
I thought she had been corrupted by demonic energy

14:12.590 --> 14:13.450
and wanted to help her.

14:13.870 --> 14:15.180
But she attacked me.

14:15.510 --> 14:16.210
The technique was strange.

14:16.630 --> 14:17.900
Nothing like what we practice here.

14:20.630 --> 14:21.850
You're projecting!

14:22.660 --> 14:23.900
If you thought something was wrong with me,

14:24.110 --> 14:25.570
why didn't you use the Linglong Talisman to summon our sect members

14:25.590 --> 14:26.610
instead of knocking me out?

14:29.680 --> 14:30.730
Oh my!

14:31.470 --> 14:32.690
You all heard that, right?

14:32.920 --> 14:34.690
My disciple was knocked out by him!

14:36.560 --> 14:37.060
Lifei,

14:37.560 --> 14:39.490
are you still feeling unwell?

14:40.320 --> 14:41.300
Yes, Master.

14:41.630 --> 14:42.450
You have no idea.

14:42.920 --> 14:44.850
My head is still spinning.

14:45.400 --> 14:46.690
See?

14:47.160 --> 14:47.540
Why

14:47.920 --> 14:49.140
did you knock out Lifei?

14:49.160 --> 14:50.020
What were you trying to do?

14:50.320 --> 14:50.900
Elder Chongyi,

14:51.710 --> 14:52.540
you can't trust

14:52.560 --> 14:53.300
the words of a spy.

14:53.990 --> 14:56.210
Qin's ability and character

14:56.990 --> 14:58.900
are well known to everyone.

14:59.590 --> 15:01.780
If he truly had feelings for Jiang,

15:02.830 --> 15:05.210
he wouldn't need to resort to such tricks.

15:07.350 --> 15:10.970
Perhaps someone was seducing him.

15:11.590 --> 15:13.020
Guangwei, Baifu,

15:13.470 --> 15:14.900
are you bullying us just because

15:14.940 --> 15:16.570
we have fewer people on Zhuiyu Peak?

15:20.870 --> 15:21.450
Qin,

15:22.230 --> 15:23.850
how are you so sure that Lifei

15:23.870 --> 15:25.540
is a demon spy?

15:26.300 --> 15:27.330
She can absorb spirit energy.

15:27.590 --> 15:29.330
Just like that traitor's evil spirit-draining technique.

15:40.630 --> 15:41.180
Elder Cuixuan,

15:42.590 --> 15:44.060
if Lifei were truly a demon spy,

15:44.420 --> 15:45.300
would she have risked her life

15:45.510 --> 15:46.380
fighting Zhuyan?

15:47.940 --> 15:48.780
Yue was there too.

15:49.510 --> 15:50.570
Please tell everyone

15:51.180 --> 15:52.810
what happened, Yue.

16:09.510 --> 16:13.490
I was knocked unconscious by Zhuyan.

16:14.460 --> 16:17.090
When I woke up, Zhuyan had already fled.

16:18.100 --> 16:19.570
I don't know

16:21.420 --> 16:22.330
what happened in between.

16:23.460 --> 16:23.900
You...

16:43.820 --> 16:45.090
Here's the thing.

16:45.580 --> 16:46.940
Lifei's techniques

16:47.110 --> 16:48.810
were all taught by me.

16:49.180 --> 16:51.300
Some of them are indeed a bit unconventional.

16:52.110 --> 16:53.850
As for absorbing spirit power,

16:55.060 --> 16:55.780
Qin,

16:56.060 --> 16:57.780
you must be mistaken.

16:58.510 --> 17:00.090
Ever since Lifei absorbed

17:00.110 --> 17:01.780
the Achillea Bead's spirit power,

17:02.100 --> 17:04.780
she's had trouble controlling the energy inside her.

17:05.350 --> 17:07.260
So Qin was likely injured

17:07.350 --> 17:11.050
by the Achillea Bead's power.

17:11.660 --> 17:12.730
It's a misunderstanding.

17:14.460 --> 17:16.530
Since both sides stick to their own stories,

17:16.900 --> 17:18.730
let's take this to the punishment hall.

17:19.460 --> 17:20.620
Truth

17:21.070 --> 17:22.340
will reveal itself then.

17:23.660 --> 17:24.250
Cuixuan.

17:26.860 --> 17:27.970
I have a way

17:28.310 --> 17:29.180
to find out the truth.

17:35.420 --> 17:37.380
Are you willing to try?

17:38.700 --> 17:39.180
I am.

17:41.990 --> 17:42.490
So...

17:42.940 --> 17:43.660
So am I.

17:51.700 --> 17:55.100
I recently came across a Lingzhi.

17:56.700 --> 17:58.050
It has a peculiar effect.

17:58.980 --> 18:01.580
It makes people speak the truth.

18:09.420 --> 18:11.100
Lifei, you go first.

18:25.710 --> 18:26.340
Lifei,

18:26.980 --> 18:28.900
how did you meet Qin Yangling?

18:33.310 --> 18:35.860
Qin said he wanted to heal me.

18:36.310 --> 18:37.770
I wanted to use the Linglong Talisman,

18:38.420 --> 18:39.940
but he tried to knock me out.

18:40.860 --> 18:41.580
And he said

18:41.940 --> 18:43.290
if I agreed to be with him,

18:43.710 --> 18:45.580
when he became the head of Wuyue Court someday,

18:46.030 --> 18:47.340
I'd stand above all others.

18:47.860 --> 18:50.340
I tried to fight back, and he ran off.

19:18.940 --> 19:19.490
Elder Dongyang,

19:19.940 --> 19:20.420
Master,

19:20.980 --> 19:21.770
I was wrong.

19:23.310 --> 19:25.180
But I really was trying to heal Lifei.

19:25.550 --> 19:27.690
Somehow, I was overcome by dark thoughts.

19:27.990 --> 19:29.340
I don't know what came over me.

19:29.470 --> 19:30.530
And I don't know why

19:30.550 --> 19:32.010
I have come to covet Lifei.

19:33.510 --> 19:35.180
What did you do to Lifei?

19:35.750 --> 19:36.210
Speak!

19:38.120 --> 19:38.690
Speak!

19:39.470 --> 19:41.010
You admit you assaulted Lifei?

19:43.030 --> 19:43.450
I...

19:43.900 --> 19:45.420
I don't remember.

19:45.660 --> 19:46.580
You wretch!

19:47.030 --> 19:48.490
I'll strip your cultivation right now!

19:50.510 --> 19:51.580
Cuixuan, calm down!

19:52.030 --> 19:54.180
Qin has always been upright.

19:54.790 --> 19:57.100
It must be the overwhelming demonic energy within the valley

19:57.470 --> 19:59.340
that made him lose his mind.

20:00.270 --> 20:03.900
This could be the work of the demon spy as well.

20:04.550 --> 20:05.730
Demons are cunning and deceitful.

20:06.070 --> 20:07.140
Before we get to the bottom of this,

20:07.420 --> 20:09.100
we must not fall for their tricks

20:09.220 --> 20:10.140
and weaken our own ranks.

20:12.030 --> 20:12.730
Fine.

20:13.470 --> 20:14.820
Very well.

20:15.310 --> 20:16.010
Let's

20:16.470 --> 20:18.340
just pretend Lifei

20:18.660 --> 20:20.620
was never wronged

20:21.030 --> 20:23.180
or mistreated.

20:23.310 --> 20:24.900
Let's just drop it!

20:38.620 --> 20:39.940
Your resolve was weak,

20:40.460 --> 20:42.210
so the demons took advantage!

20:43.660 --> 20:44.900
Go to Yunhai Peak now

20:45.180 --> 20:46.050
for punishment and reflection!

20:58.710 --> 21:00.180
The demon beast Zhuyan has escaped.

21:00.700 --> 21:01.770
Notify all nine states' sects

21:02.070 --> 21:04.100
to spare no effort in tracking it down!

21:47.990 --> 21:48.490
Who's there?

22:02.120 --> 22:03.250
Lei Xiuyuan?

22:04.470 --> 22:05.180
What are you doing?

22:10.120 --> 22:10.860
I said

22:12.180 --> 22:13.380
anyone who dares to hurt Lifei

22:14.790 --> 22:15.660
will die by my hand.

22:30.990 --> 22:33.250
Lei, I didn't mean it.

22:54.230 --> 22:55.100
If you kill me,

22:55.700 --> 22:57.690
the elders won't let you go.

22:58.360 --> 23:00.860
And it'll drag Lifei into it.

23:01.230 --> 23:01.730
Shut up!

23:03.860 --> 23:04.770
You don't deserve to say her name.

23:11.420 --> 23:12.860
How do you have demonic energy on you?

23:17.700 --> 23:18.180
No.

23:20.510 --> 23:21.770
You were tainted by demonic energy

23:22.940 --> 23:23.900
and went berserk,

23:24.860 --> 23:27.250
and I was forced to kill you

23:27.660 --> 23:28.970
to root out the demon spy.

23:30.940 --> 23:31.620
Die!

24:03.470 --> 24:04.970
You dare bully my disciple?

24:05.180 --> 24:06.450
You're asking for it!

24:06.660 --> 24:07.290
He deserves to die.

24:08.550 --> 24:09.450
Sir, why are you stopping me?

24:13.270 --> 24:15.860
Cuixuan is already suspicious

24:15.900 --> 24:17.340
of you and Lifei.

24:17.990 --> 24:20.820
Just don't stir up more trouble, alright?

24:26.710 --> 24:27.970
Did you pick up

24:28.620 --> 24:30.180
some demonic energy in Lilie Valley too?

24:34.660 --> 24:37.140
Go back and expel it with your cultivation.

24:41.180 --> 24:42.690
That snake Qin Yangling.

24:42.990 --> 24:44.530
He hid his true colors so well all along.

24:45.270 --> 24:47.010
Elder Cuixuan is obviously protecting his own.

24:47.990 --> 24:49.100
And worst of all,

24:49.620 --> 24:52.010
they even accused Lifei of seducing him.

24:53.100 --> 24:54.340
Come on, look at Lifei,

24:54.510 --> 24:55.730
who could she even seduce?

24:58.510 --> 24:59.250
Lifei, take it easy.

24:59.270 --> 24:59.860
Drink slowly.

25:00.200 --> 25:00.860
There's more in the kitchen.

25:03.400 --> 25:04.820
Appearances are deceptive.

25:05.510 --> 25:06.860
Lei Xiuyuan is a good one, though.

25:07.470 --> 25:09.860
He stood up to protect you just now.

25:14.200 --> 25:15.620
If Lifei were truly a demon spy,

25:15.750 --> 25:16.730
would she have risked her life?

25:16.960 --> 25:17.660
Lifei,

25:17.990 --> 25:20.050
how did you and Lei run into Zhuyan?

25:20.440 --> 25:22.420
And how did it escape later?

25:22.880 --> 25:23.820
We just ran into it.

25:24.340 --> 25:25.620
Then, when everyone showed up,

25:25.710 --> 25:26.530
it ran off.

25:29.600 --> 25:31.290
Have you ever considered this?

25:32.160 --> 25:33.690
Without a spy helping from the inside,

25:33.880 --> 25:36.340
how did that scumbag Zhuyan escape?

25:40.030 --> 25:42.420
You all know Zhuyan, right?

25:43.600 --> 25:46.290
It's one of the four great demon beasts.

25:47.270 --> 25:48.380
With it on the loose,

25:48.880 --> 25:51.860
who knows how many sect disciples will suffer?

25:54.070 --> 25:56.010
Peaceful days are over.

26:07.550 --> 26:08.050
Xiuyuan.

26:27.960 --> 26:28.420
Lifei?

26:31.750 --> 26:32.580
I came to ask you something.

26:32.920 --> 26:33.580
Don't overthink it.

26:37.070 --> 26:37.660
Go ahead.

26:43.070 --> 26:44.340
Are you hiding something from me?

26:48.710 --> 26:50.100
That time in the academy's forbidden area.

26:50.840 --> 26:51.620
And this time too.

26:54.230 --> 26:55.820
Every time you're corrupted by demonic energy,

26:56.440 --> 26:57.820
you react strangely.

26:59.640 --> 27:00.450
And

27:01.880 --> 27:02.900
your eyes

27:05.030 --> 27:06.100
turn golden.

27:08.230 --> 27:09.530
And at the Altar of Martyrs.

27:10.310 --> 27:11.250
Were those skulls

27:11.840 --> 27:13.100
and black demon spirits

27:13.840 --> 27:15.100
summoned by you?

27:27.550 --> 27:28.210
Fine, don't tell me.

27:29.340 --> 27:30.660
Anyway, after Lilie Valley,

27:31.790 --> 27:32.860
we're even.

27:33.440 --> 27:34.730
Let's just stay out of each other's way

27:34.990 --> 27:36.010
and keep our distance.

27:44.790 --> 27:45.860
I've been a spirit magnet since childhood.

27:46.340 --> 27:47.340
I'm not like others.

27:47.790 --> 27:48.580
My master said

27:49.200 --> 27:50.940
that no two people are exactly alike.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.420
No need to force everyone to be the same.

27:54.880 --> 27:55.820
Watch out for yourself.

28:01.790 --> 28:02.180
Lifei.

28:03.680 --> 28:04.420
Leave with me.

28:06.600 --> 28:07.250
What did you say?

28:07.790 --> 28:08.420
Let's leave together.

28:08.600 --> 28:09.210
Go back to Qingqiu.

28:09.960 --> 28:11.140
The Sea Calamity and the demons

28:11.960 --> 28:12.730
have nothing to do with us.

28:14.030 --> 28:15.250
You're talking nonsense. Let go.

28:15.640 --> 28:16.490
Lifei, you said

28:17.440 --> 28:18.210
you didn't want to be bullied.

28:18.990 --> 28:20.380
You want to sleep soundly and live freely.

28:21.440 --> 28:22.940
But we're not living freely here.

28:23.790 --> 28:24.690
Your senior brother isn't here.

28:24.710 --> 28:25.580
Your master isn't here.

28:26.440 --> 28:27.340
Why stay?

28:30.030 --> 28:30.660
Let's leave together.

28:35.070 --> 28:36.010
I won't hurt you again.

28:37.840 --> 28:38.620
We'll leave now.

28:43.120 --> 28:43.620
Let go...

28:50.680 --> 28:51.660
How dare you, you wretch!

28:52.200 --> 28:54.010
Are you trying to follow in Hu Jiaping's footsteps?

29:01.960 --> 29:02.450
Well,

29:02.960 --> 29:03.660
sir,

29:04.160 --> 29:05.660
Elder Dongyang's medicine for Lei

29:05.680 --> 29:06.250
has been delivered.

29:06.270 --> 29:07.210
I'll be leaving now.

29:17.880 --> 29:19.380
You're blinded by lust

29:19.400 --> 29:20.450
and refuse to learn.

29:21.440 --> 29:23.050
I'd rather strip your cultivation myself

29:23.710 --> 29:25.730
than let you betray the sect

29:25.750 --> 29:27.210
like Hu Jiaping.

29:29.840 --> 29:32.420
Reflect on yourself here.

30:06.400 --> 30:08.180
Can't you control her?

30:08.790 --> 30:10.140
First, she messed with Qin

30:10.750 --> 30:12.140
and got him banished to Yunhai Peak.

30:12.600 --> 30:15.490
Now she is targeting my disciple at Yaogang Peak

30:15.600 --> 30:17.730
and nearly talked him into eloping!

30:19.750 --> 30:21.180
Guangwei,

30:21.440 --> 30:23.580
how can you say that?

30:24.120 --> 30:26.180
She was just visiting him out of concern.

30:27.360 --> 30:28.140
Spare me!

30:28.600 --> 30:29.290
I'm telling you,

30:29.920 --> 30:31.380
tell Jiang Lifei

30:31.510 --> 30:33.100
to stay away from Yaoguang Peak!

30:33.400 --> 30:33.940
I can't control that.

30:34.470 --> 30:36.050
Young people's affairs are beyond me.

30:36.750 --> 30:38.010
I can't just lock my disciple up

30:38.030 --> 30:40.100
in Danxue every time like you do.

30:40.400 --> 30:42.450
Your disciple can be content with mediocrity.

30:42.750 --> 30:44.290
But Lei Xiuyuan carries great responsibility.

30:44.550 --> 30:46.730
I don't want to see him expelled!

30:47.120 --> 30:48.100
Then expel him.

30:48.230 --> 30:49.210
I'll take him.

30:49.710 --> 30:51.380
He's here often enough anyway.

30:53.470 --> 30:54.340
Chongyi,

30:55.270 --> 30:56.620
the Sea Calamity is coming.

30:56.880 --> 30:58.730
How long can you shield them?

30:59.990 --> 31:02.580
Have you forgotten what happened 500 years ago?

31:03.750 --> 31:05.490
When we're gone,

31:05.640 --> 31:07.050
who will protect them?

31:07.440 --> 31:09.340
Only through dedicated cultivation

31:10.120 --> 31:12.340
can we truly help them.

31:14.640 --> 31:16.100
Jiang Lifei has a unique constitution.

31:16.790 --> 31:18.010
She's your disciple.

31:18.030 --> 31:20.050
It's fine if you want to protect her.

31:21.550 --> 31:23.050
But can you really not see

31:24.070 --> 31:25.580
that she's different from others?

31:27.400 --> 31:28.420
When the Sea Calamity comes,

31:28.750 --> 31:30.580
creatures across the sea will invade the Central Plains.

31:30.840 --> 31:31.380
Suspicion

31:31.680 --> 31:32.860
will spread among the people.

31:33.070 --> 31:35.140
Who will be able to protect her then?

31:41.960 --> 31:43.100
Across the sea?

31:55.070 --> 31:56.010
Golden eyes?

31:56.920 --> 31:57.690
Spirit-attracting?

31:59.030 --> 32:00.580
Are there such constitutions across the sea?

32:04.880 --> 32:05.420
Gelin.

32:08.230 --> 32:09.210
Why aren't you training?

32:10.070 --> 32:11.050
Why train?

32:13.750 --> 32:14.380
Might as well end it all.

32:14.990 --> 32:15.820
Why waste the time?

32:16.440 --> 32:17.620
Since you haven't made up your mind,

32:18.360 --> 32:19.180
live each day

32:19.510 --> 32:20.490
to the fullest.

32:21.840 --> 32:22.970
Whether life is long or short,

32:23.750 --> 32:24.580
it should be lived without regret.

32:25.440 --> 32:26.340
What are you talking about,

32:26.360 --> 32:26.970
Lu?

32:27.680 --> 32:28.530
I'm still young,

32:28.550 --> 32:29.250
and you're cursing me to die?

32:30.360 --> 32:31.250
You're not going to try... again?

32:31.400 --> 32:33.140
I mean, I can already summon spirits.

32:33.960 --> 32:35.050
More training is just a waste of time.

32:37.030 --> 32:38.620
Spirit summoning is the hardest technique of the Sea Sect.

32:39.310 --> 32:39.970
You really mastered it?

32:41.960 --> 32:42.820
You don't believe me?

32:44.550 --> 32:45.140
How about this?

32:45.680 --> 32:46.420
Let's make a bet.

32:47.070 --> 32:48.210
If I've really mastered it,

32:49.070 --> 32:49.970
you give me something.

32:52.230 --> 32:52.660
Deal.

33:19.990 --> 33:20.620
Lu,

33:21.030 --> 33:22.050
that pendant of yours is nice.

33:22.310 --> 33:23.010
Give it to me.

33:26.440 --> 33:27.180
Are you sure you want it?

33:39.550 --> 33:40.050
I...

33:40.600 --> 33:41.690
I was joking.

33:45.550 --> 33:46.340
Oh, Lu,

33:46.960 --> 33:47.970
do you know if anyone

33:47.990 --> 33:49.420
across the sea has golden eyes?

33:49.840 --> 33:50.860
Or a spirit-attracting constitution?

33:52.750 --> 33:53.820
I don't know about spirit-attracting.

33:54.640 --> 33:55.490
But golden eyes...

33:57.750 --> 33:58.970
They say the Demon Lord Yecha

33:59.310 --> 34:00.180
had golden eyes.

34:05.960 --> 34:07.210
Demon Lord Yecha?

34:08.230 --> 34:08.620
Wait,

34:09.440 --> 34:10.380
the Demon Lord is hideous.

34:10.400 --> 34:12.130
How could Lei Xiuyuan be him?

34:13.150 --> 34:14.820
Gelin probably got it wrong.

34:15.880 --> 34:16.380
Forget it.

34:16.590 --> 34:17.380
I'll look it up myself.

34:19.760 --> 34:20.340
Oh, right,

34:21.280 --> 34:23.050
Master has a book about the lands across the sea.

34:33.670 --> 34:34.490
What's that sound?

34:37.700 --> 34:39.530
Cuixuan, the Pangu Bell is ringing.

34:39.920 --> 34:40.940
Has something big happened?

34:42.760 --> 34:44.450
The disciples tracking Zhuyan report

34:44.700 --> 34:47.130
that it has broken into the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff.

34:49.980 --> 34:50.820
I knew

34:51.110 --> 34:52.220
that Outcast Tomb across the sea

34:52.470 --> 34:53.740
would eventually bring disaster.

34:54.240 --> 34:55.010
If only back then...

34:55.510 --> 34:56.940
Don't bring up the past.

34:57.780 --> 34:59.820
The Outcast Tomb has been sealed for centuries,

35:00.070 --> 35:01.820
and no one has set foot there.

35:02.510 --> 35:04.090
Even those who stumbled in

35:04.380 --> 35:05.780
never came back.

35:06.240 --> 35:07.820
No one knows

35:08.510 --> 35:09.860
what's inside to this day.

35:10.240 --> 35:12.650
After all that effort to dodge the immortal sects' pursuit,

35:13.030 --> 35:14.570
Zhuyan fought its way into the Outcast Tomb.

35:14.990 --> 35:15.820
Why?

35:21.030 --> 35:23.530
The Outcast Tomb is full of traps.

35:24.300 --> 35:25.780
Perhaps the most dangerous place

35:26.240 --> 35:28.380
is the safest in the entire Central Plains.

35:28.820 --> 35:29.340
That

35:29.670 --> 35:31.450
could be the demons' stronghold.

35:40.670 --> 35:41.740
This is a serious matter.

35:42.550 --> 35:44.220
Whether it's a stronghold

35:44.900 --> 35:46.450
or a trap,

35:47.820 --> 35:50.260
I'm going there myself

35:50.820 --> 35:53.010
to get to the bottom of it.

35:55.860 --> 35:56.700
Lifei.

35:57.590 --> 35:58.340
Lifei?

36:15.030 --> 36:15.650
Lifei?

36:26.550 --> 36:27.420
Enjoy reading it?

36:28.190 --> 36:30.260
Can't read a character of it. What is all this?

36:34.030 --> 36:34.860
Master.

36:36.240 --> 36:37.300
Silly girl.

36:37.420 --> 36:38.130
What book is that?

36:38.380 --> 36:39.130
You were so absorbed

36:39.150 --> 36:40.300
that you didn't even notice me come in.

36:41.900 --> 36:43.380
I picked it up by the roadside somewhere.

36:44.340 --> 36:45.780
The demons across the sea are about to invade.

36:45.820 --> 36:46.530
So I'm doing some research.

36:50.420 --> 36:51.420
You can read this?

36:51.460 --> 36:52.940
I can read anything.

36:55.190 --> 36:57.860
You know, this book

36:58.980 --> 37:00.340
is quite detailed.

37:00.860 --> 37:02.820
It even covers secret histories

37:02.860 --> 37:04.940
like the Outcast Tomb across the sea.

37:05.240 --> 37:06.530
Outcast Tomb?

37:07.030 --> 37:07.860
What place is that?

37:13.190 --> 37:14.780
That's actually why

37:14.820 --> 37:16.010
I came to see you today.

37:16.420 --> 37:18.490
Remember that Zhuyan who escaped

37:18.510 --> 37:19.380
a while back?

37:20.720 --> 37:22.010
That scumbag

37:22.630 --> 37:24.610
has holed up in the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff.

37:25.070 --> 37:26.860
Cuixuan wants to

37:27.380 --> 37:29.820
take a group of elite disciples there.

37:30.460 --> 37:32.650
Do you think you'd be left out?

37:33.190 --> 37:33.860
So

37:34.340 --> 37:37.650
I think you need to fall sick starting today

37:38.030 --> 37:39.570
and stay sick until they get back.

37:40.550 --> 37:41.260
Get it?

37:43.780 --> 37:45.260
Master is tied to the world across the sea.

37:46.240 --> 37:48.090
I should take this chance to find out more.

37:49.380 --> 37:50.260
We are facing a massive threat.

37:51.110 --> 37:52.610
How can I pretend to be sick and hide?

37:53.150 --> 37:54.970
What's with the outburst? Have you lost your mind?

37:55.460 --> 37:56.780
Last time it was for the Achillea Bead.

37:56.980 --> 37:57.740
What is it this time?

37:59.380 --> 38:00.220
Master,

38:00.820 --> 38:02.220
you just said

38:02.670 --> 38:03.650
all the disciples are going.

38:04.240 --> 38:05.340
So Lei Xiuyuan will be going too.

38:05.980 --> 38:07.300
How can I miss that?

38:10.990 --> 38:13.530
I feel like I'm losing control over you.

38:16.110 --> 38:16.740
Fine.

38:16.940 --> 38:19.010
I'll give you a protective sword.

38:28.980 --> 38:29.860
White Cliff is dangerous.

38:30.460 --> 38:31.610
Be careful in everything.

38:32.150 --> 38:33.970
If you run into something you can't handle,

38:34.420 --> 38:35.490
don't push yourself.

38:35.510 --> 38:36.260
Run straight back

38:36.550 --> 38:38.010
to Zhuiyu Peak.

38:38.070 --> 38:38.570
Remember,

38:38.860 --> 38:40.090
once you're back here,

38:40.630 --> 38:42.450
no one can hurt you.

39:19.860 --> 39:20.940
Still won't admit you're wrong?

39:21.900 --> 39:24.860
Do you really want me to destroy your spirit root

39:24.900 --> 39:26.260
and strip your cultivation?

39:26.780 --> 39:27.530
I'm not wrong.

39:28.860 --> 39:29.450
Why should I admit it?

39:52.590 --> 39:54.220
Zhuyan has fled to White Cliff.

39:54.880 --> 39:56.090
Go with Cuixuan

39:56.800 --> 39:57.970
and make up for your mistake.

40:10.700 --> 40:11.490
Come in,

40:12.220 --> 40:12.940
Lei.

40:39.550 --> 40:40.780
Why did Zhuyan head to White Cliff?

40:42.960 --> 40:44.130
How would I know?

40:44.920 --> 40:45.900
You let it out.

40:46.800 --> 40:47.420
How can you not know?

40:50.980 --> 40:52.860
Zhuyan's chains were deliberately cut.

40:54.110 --> 40:54.860
You called for help,

40:55.470 --> 40:56.340
but your breathing was steady

40:56.920 --> 40:57.900
and didn't falter for a second.

40:59.630 --> 41:00.650
And that last whistle

41:01.360 --> 41:01.970
was you too.

41:05.590 --> 41:06.260
Yue,

41:07.440 --> 41:08.530
what are you after?

41:11.150 --> 41:12.220
What am I after?

41:14.440 --> 41:15.780
You, of course.

41:22.110 --> 41:23.010
Who are you really?

41:24.280 --> 41:25.940
When you reach White Cliff,

41:26.360 --> 41:27.650
you'll know everything.

41:31.320 --> 41:33.260
Aren't you afraid I'll tell Master all of this?

41:41.800 --> 41:42.650
I know

41:44.150 --> 41:44.970
you won't.

42:26.400 --> 42:27.340
He's here too.

42:28.220 --> 42:29.220
What a pain.

42:29.700 --> 42:31.090
He's done reflecting already?

42:31.470 --> 42:33.090
He's trying to make up for his mistake

42:33.110 --> 42:34.300
and make this all go away.

42:34.800 --> 42:36.780
No wonder my divination last night warned me

42:37.320 --> 42:38.570
about a backstabber on this trip.

42:42.200 --> 42:42.920
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.920 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
